Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: New York financial crisis
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040brvl
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 9 Apr 1978
New York hoping for Washington aid to tackle city's mounting financial crisis. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.